---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Prom & Graduation Lash Specials | Orange County"
  description="Special lash packages for prom, graduation, and senior photos in Orange County. Look stunning for your special milestone events!"
  keywords="prom lashes Orange County, graduation lash extensions, senior photo lashes, teen lash specials OC"
>
  <Navigation />
  <main class="pt-20 bg-lightbg">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
        </svg>
        Back to Blog
      </a>
      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="text-sm text-primary font-medium mb-4">August 9, 2025</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-playfair text-darktext mb-6">Prom & Graduation Lash Specials</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-mediumtext">Look absolutely stunning for prom, graduation, and senior photos with our special student lash packages!</p>
      </header>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>Your prom and graduation are once-in-a-lifetime moments that deserve to be picture-perfect! At Elegant Lashes by Katie, we specialize in creating gorgeous lash looks for Orange County high school students celebrating these milestone events. Our special student packages ensure you look absolutely stunning from your first photo to your last dance!</p>

        <h2>Prom Lash Packages</h2>
        <h3>Classic Prom Package</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Full set of beautiful lash extensions</li>
          <li>Style consultation to match your dress</li>
          <li>Applied 2-3 days before prom for perfection</li>
          <li>Lasts through after-prom activities</li>
          <li>Special student pricing with valid ID</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Glam Prom Package</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Volume lash set for maximum drama</li>
          <li>Custom design for your prom theme</li>
          <li>Perfect for photos and videos</li>
          <li>Complimentary touch-up within 48 hours</li>
          <li>Premium student discount</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Graduation Lash Specials</h2>
        <p>Look amazing walking across that stage and in all your graduation photos:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Natural enhancement that photographs beautifully</li>
          <li>Lasts through graduation day and celebrations</li>
          <li>Perfect under your cap and in outdoor lighting</li>
          <li>Group discounts for graduating friends</li>
          <li>Available at all Orange County locations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Senior Photo Packages</h2>
        <p>Your senior photos last forever - make sure your lashes look perfect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Camera-ready lash extensions</li>
          <li>Natural to dramatic styles available</li>
          <li>Coordinates with your photo outfits</li>
          <li>Lasts through multiple photo sessions</li>
          <li>Special package pricing for seniors</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Orange County Students Love Our Lash Specials</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Affordable student pricing</li>
          <li>No-smudge, waterproof for happy tears</li>
          <li>Lasts through long event days</li>
          <li>Looks perfect in professional photos</li>
          <li>Parent-approved professional application</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Group Discounts</h2>
        <p>Going to prom with friends? Get lashes together and save!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>3-5 friends: 15% off each</li>
          <li>6-9 friends: 20% off each</li>
          <li>10+ group: 25% off each</li>
          <li>Coordinated appointments available</li>
          <li>Fun group lash party atmosphere</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Parent-Approved Safety</h2>
        <p>Parents love that we:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use professional, medical-grade products</li>
          <li>Employ only certified, licensed artists</li>
          <li>Maintain impeccable hygiene standards</li>
          <li>Provide thorough consultation and care instructions</li>
          <li>Offer parental consultation if desired</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Book Your Student Lash Appointment</h2>
        <p>Don't wait until the last minute! Prom and graduation season books up quickly at our Irvine, Tustin, Santa Ana, and Costa Mesa locations. Reserve your spot today and ensure you look absolutely stunning for your big day!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-sunset p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-playfair text-darktext mb-4">Ready for Your Special Event?</h3>
        <p class="text-darktext mb-6">Book your student lash special in Irvine, Tustin, Santa Ana, or Costa Mesa!</p>
        <button type="button" class="open-modal-button main-book-now-btn text-xl">
          <span>Book Student Special</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
<style>
  .prose { color: #8A7584; }
  .prose h2 { color: #221439; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .prose h3 { color: #AC5F77; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .prose ul { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; list-style-type: disc; }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose strong { color: #221439; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
